               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18400203-name-514" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-514" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-514" type="surname" value="HORWILL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-514" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES HORWILL</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a cheesemonger's shop in Moor-street, Soho. On the 3rd of February 1 was sitting in the parlour, and heard the window fall—I looked, and saw Manning holding the window up with his right hand, and there were five or six boys round—I went out, and Manning dropped a piece of bacon while I was pursuing him—there was 6lbs. 14oz. weight of bacon found in all.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
