                        <interp inst="t18400203-name-515" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL WOOD</persName>
                  </hi>. I was coming down the street—I heard a cry of "Stop thief!" Jones ran into my arms, and dropped three pieces of bacon at my feet—I took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Jones's Defence</hi>. I saw a lot of people, and the man laid hold of me.</p>
